Authors: Pradeep Tyagi, Katsumi Kadekawa, Mahendra Kashyap, Subrata Pore, Naoki Yoshimura
Title: Spontaneous Recovery of Reflex Voiding Following Spinal Cord Injury Mediated by Anti-inflammatory and Neuroprotective Factors
Abstract: OBJECTIVE To investigate the time-dependent changes in expression of cytokines that characterizes the spontaneous recovery of reflex voiding after spinal cord injury (SCI). SCI is known to reorganize the neural circuitry of micturition reflex after injury.
